    output: processed_data/GAFexonReduced/TCGA-DX-A2J4-01A-32D-A21Q-09.broadgaf.wig.exome.reduced.maf
    jobid: 769
    wildcards: exome_id=TCGA-DX-A2J4-01A-32D-A21Q-09


        bedtools intersect \
            -b /diskmnt/Projects/ICGC_MC3/Coverage_Reduction/TCGA-DX-A2J4-01A-32D-A21Q-09.bed \
            -a processed_data/GAFexon/TCGA-DX-A2J4-01A-32D-A21Q-09.exome.broadgaf.maf \
            -wb | \
        awk -F"\t" '{OFS = "\t"} {if($NF == 1) print $0}' \
        > processed_data/GAFexonReduced/TCGA-DX-A2J4-01A-32D-A21Q-09.broadgaf.wig.exome.reduced.maf

    output: processed_data/GAFexonReduced/TCGA-CV-5432-01A-02D-1683-08.broadgaf.wig.exome.reduced.maf
    jobid: 1049
    wildcards: exome_id=TCGA-CV-5432-01A-02D-1683-08


        bedtools intersect \
            -b /diskmnt/Projects/ICGC_MC3/Coverage_Reduction/TCGA-CV-5432-01A-02D-1683-08.bed \
            -a processed_data/GAFexon/TCGA-CV-5432-01A-02D-1683-08.exome.broadgaf.maf \
            -wb | \
        awk -F"\t" '{OFS = "\t"} {if($NF == 1) print $0}' \
        > processed_data/GAFexonReduced/TCGA-CV-5432-01A-02D-1683-08.broadgaf.wig.exome.reduced.maf

    output: processed_data/GAFexonReduced/TCGA-EP-A26S-01A-11D-A16V-10.broadgaf.wig.exome.reduced.maf
    jobid: 1461
    wildcards: exome_id=TCGA-EP-A26S-01A-11D-A16V-10


        bedtools intersect \
            -b /diskmnt/Projects/ICGC_MC3/Coverage_Reduction/TCGA-EP-A26S-01A-11D-A16V-10.bed \
            -a processed_data/GAFexon/TCGA-EP-A26S-01A-11D-A16V-10.exome.broadgaf.maf \
            -wb | \
        awk -F"\t" '{OFS = "\t"} {if($NF == 1) print $0}' \
        > processed_data/GAFexonReduced/TCGA-EP-A26S-01A-11D-A16V-10.broadgaf.wig.exome.reduced.maf

    output: processed_data/GAFexonReduced/DO9106.broadgaf.wig.genome.reduced.maf
    jobid: 560
    wildcards: genome_id=DO9106


        bedtools intersect \
            -b /diskmnt/Projects/ICGC_MC3/Coverage_Reduction/TCGA-AA-A01S-01A-21W-A096-10.bed \
            -a processed_data/GAFexon/DO9106.genome.broadgaf.maf \
            -wb | \
        awk -F"\t" '{OFS = "\t"} {if($NF == 1) print $0}' \
        > processed_data/GAFexonReduced/DO9106.broadgaf.wig.genome.reduced.maf

    output: processed_data/GAFexonReduced/TCGA-EM-A2OW-01A-11D-A202-08.broadgaf.wig.exome.reduced.maf
    jobid: 1022
    wildcards: exome_id=TCGA-EM-A2OW-01A-11D-A202-08


        bedtools intersect \
            -b /diskmnt/Projects/ICGC_MC3/Coverage_Reduction/TCGA-EM-A2OW-01A-11D-A202-08.bed \
            -a processed_data/GAFexon/TCGA-EM-A2OW-01A-11D-A202-08.exome.broadgaf.maf \
            -wb | \
        awk -F"\t" '{OFS = "\t"} {if($NF == 1) print $0}' \
        > processed_data/GAFexonReduced/TCGA-EM-A2OW-01A-11D-A202-08.broadgaf.wig.exome.reduced.maf

    output: processed_data/GAFexonReduced/TCGA-B0-5693-01A-11D-1534-10.broadgaf.wig.exome.reduced.maf
    jobid: 854
    wildcards: exome_id=TCGA-B0-5693-01A-11D-1534-10


        bedtools intersect \
            -b /diskmnt/Projects/ICGC_MC3/Coverage_Reduction/TCGA-B0-5693-01A-11D-1534-10.bed \
            -a processed_data/GAFexon/TCGA-B0-5693-01A-11D-1534-10.exome.broadgaf.maf \
            -wb | \
        awk -F"\t" '{OFS = "\t"} {if($NF == 1) print $0}' \
        > processed_data/GAFexonReduced/TCGA-B0-5693-01A-11D-1534-10.broadgaf.wig.exome.reduced.maf

rule reduce_maf_low_genome_wig:
    input: processed_data/exome.broadbed.gafe.wigs.maf, processed_data/fake_icgc46.wig.bed
    output: processed_data/exome.broadbed.gafe.wigs.rep.maf
    jobid: 6
    wildcards: seq_type=exome

bedtools intersect -a processed_data/exome.broadbed.gafe.wigs.maf -b processed_data/fake_icgc46.wig.bed | sort -u > processed_data/exome.broadbed.gafe.wigs.rep.maf

rule reduce_maf_low_genome_wig:
    input: processed_data/genome.broadbed.gafe.wigs.maf, processed_data/fake_icgc46.wig.bed
    output: processed_data/genome.broadbed.gafe.wigs.rep.maf
    jobid: 5
    wildcards: seq_type=genome

bedtools intersect -a processed_data/genome.broadbed.gafe.wigs.maf -b processed_data/fake_icgc46.wig.bed | sort -u > processed_data/genome.broadbed.gafe.wigs.rep.maf

rule reduce_maf_low_genome_wig_uniq_snv:
    input: processed_data/genome.broadbed.gafe.wigs.rep.maf
    output: processed_data/genome.broadbed.gafe.wigs.rep.snv.uniq.maf
    jobid: 3
    wildcards: seq_type=genome


        awk -F"\t" '{if($2 == $3) print $0}' processed_data/genome.broadbed.gafe.wigs.rep.maf \
            | sort -u | sort -k1,1 -k2,2n \
            > processed_data/genome.broadbed.gafe.wigs.rep.snv.uniq.maf
